== Access ==
; By Bus
* From [[:en:Utsunomiya Station|Utsunomiya Station]] (JR West Exit):
** Take the {{ill|Kantō Bus|ja|関東自動車|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kantō Bus|qq=|1=Kantō Bus|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11655984}} to the Teikyo University/Utsunomiya Museum of Art line (approx. 15 minutes). Alight at "Toyosatodai Entrance" and walk for 20 minutes.

; By Car
* From National Route 119 (Toyosato Bypass):
** Proceed north from the Nagaokamachi Intersection along the {{ill|Nagaoka Road|ja|長岡街道|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Nagaoka Road|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} for 3 minutes.
* From {{ill|Tochigi Prefecture Route 63|ja|栃木県道63号藤原宇都宮線|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tochigi Prefecture Route 63|qq=|1=Tochigi Prefectural Road Route 63|comment=changed title based on wikidata|WD=Q11535545}}:
** Head west from the Sekibori-cho North Intersection via Nagaoka Road for 3 minutes.

